~ start
Olivia: [[Hey|Hiya|Hey there]], I'm Olivia the one in charge of running this shop stall
Olivia: Tell me what brings you to my humble shop?
- I want to buy some stuff
	Olivia: What do you want to buy?
	- Corn seeds
		set item_name = "corn seed"
	- Tomato seeds
		set item_name = "tomato seed"
	do InventoryManager.add_collectable(item_name)

- I want to sell some of my farm products
	Olivia: Which products do you want to sell?
	- Corn
		set item_name = "corn"
	- Tomato
		set item_name = "tomato"
	- Egg
		set item_name = "egg"
	- Milk
		set item_name = "milk"
	do InventoryManager.remove_collectable(item_name)
- Never mind
=> END